      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/uk-wage-hike-to-hit-shoppers-pockets-warn-pub-and-retail-chiefs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国零售业和酒店业老板警告称，在财政大臣杰里米·亨特提高近 300 万人的工资后，物价可能会上涨。]]></description>
